snippet.title: Foragery - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Foragery on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2741480/Foragery/

Play the demo on Steam!

Complete quests, uncover secrets, and bask in the scenery with a new 2D adventure set on two different remote islands!
